Articles.Content:
At long last, I've completed my Jool-5 Challenge Mission! It took me more than a month to do (first launch was on Jan 26), mainly due to RL and other missions getting launch windows in my career save.

So, here are the images with captions. Be aware, it's pretty long; 91 images. So, sit back and enjoy.

Javascript is disabled. View full album
